pageContext.claim: “They forgot to put my name on the ballot....Other than that, the ballots were wonderful, right? These are cheaters.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump falsely claimed that about 2,000 ballots were printed in California without his name on it. Instead the ballots were missing the entire presidential race, so not only Trump's name but Joe Biden's name and the names of other candidates were also missing.The ballots were sent to a single precinct in Los Angeles and the faulty ballots were quickly replaced.
